<html>

<head>
	<title>The Stash | Staff Application Form</title>
	<!-- Bootstrap CSS -->
	<link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/latest/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">

	<!-- Bootswatch Darkly theme -->
	<link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootswatch/latest/darkly/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no">

	<!-- Custom Styles -->
	<style>
		body {
			display: flex;
			align-items: center;
			justify-content: center;
			height: 100vh;
			/* 100% of the viewport height */
			margin: 0;
		}
	</style>
	<style>
		body {
			position: relative;
			/* Adjust this value based on your footer height */
		}

		footer {
			position: absolute;
			bottom: 0;
			text-align: center;
			
			padding: 10px;
		}
	</style>
</head>

<body>
	<!-- Big ol centered text that says Success-->
	<center>
		<h1 id="success">Success!</h1>
		<p class="lead">Thank you <%= sessionData.discordData.global_name %>, your form has been submitted.</p>
		<div id="left">
			NOTICE: Do not ask about the progress of your application. </br>
			An application review date will always be specified in the Application Wave's Opening
			Announcement. Please be vigilant for any updates and/or review date extensions which may
			occur in <a
				href="https://discordapp.com/channels/896000683407458354/896002001014505472">#announcements</a>.</br>
			DO NOT SHARE THIS FORM THROUGH DM'S OR PUBLIC CHANNELS, UNLESS EXPLICITLY REQUESTED BY PROMOTIONS
			TEAM PERSONNEL OR COUNCIL MEMBERS.</br>

			Any burning questions/concerns you would like answered should be DM'd to either:</br>

			Promotions Director - Tundra (gamerhombre)</br>
			Promotions Co-Director - Council Man (suction_cup_man)</br>
			Head of In-Game Staff - Cr1tikal (cr1tikal621)</br>
			Server Owner - Oxygen (oxygen_breathableatmosphere)
		</div>
	</center>
	<script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/latest/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
	<footer>
		<p>&copy; <%= new Date().getFullYear() %> The Stash</p>
	</footer>
</body>


</html>